<footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-container">
        <!-- Top Section -->
        <div class="footer-top">
            <div class="footer-brand">
                <h2 class="brand-name">5MinuteMeds</h2>
                <p class="brand-tagline">Fast & Affordable Medication</p>
                <div class="social-links">
                    {
                        socialLinks.map((social) => (
                            <a
                                href={social.url}
                                target="_blank"
                                aria-label={social.name}
                                class="social-link"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    width="24"
                                    height="24"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    fill="currentColor"
                                >
                                    <path d={social.icon} />
                                </svg>
                            </a>
                        ))
                    }
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="legitscript-badge">
                <img
                    src="/images/legit-script.webp"
                    alt="LegitScript Certified"
                />
            </div>

            <nav class="footer-nav">
                <div class="nav-column">
                    <h3>Contact</h3>
                    <ul>
                        {
                            footerLinks.contact.map((link) => (
                                <li>
                                    <a href={link.url}>{link.text}</a>
                                </li>
                            ))
                        }
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="nav-column">
                    <h3>Learn more</h3>
                    <ul>
                        {
                            footerLinks.learnMore.map((link) => (
                                <li>
                                    <a href={link.url}>{link.text}</a>
                                </li>
                            ))
                        }
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="nav-column">
                    <h3>Legal</h3>
                    <ul>
                        {
                            footerLinks.legal.map((link) => (
                                <li>
                                    <a href={link.url}>{link.text}</a>
                                </li>
                            ))
                        }
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </div>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="footer-divider"></div>

        <!-- Disclaimers -->
        <div class="footer-disclaimers">
            <p class="disclaimer">
                Product packaging shown in images is for illustrative purposes
                only and may differ from the actual packaging customers receive.
            </p>
            <p class="disclaimer">
                Based on separate individual studies of oral minoxidil and oral finasteride.
            </p>
            <p class="disclaimer">
                *Compounded products have not been approved by the FDA. The FDA
                does not verify the safety, effectiveness, or quality of
                compounded drugs. *Prescription products require an online
                consultation with a healthcare provider who will determine if a
                prescription is appropriate. *Ozempic® (semaglutide), Wegovy®
                (semaglutide), and Mounjaro® (tirzepatide) are not compounded.
                Ozempic® and Mounjaro® are FDA-approved for type 2 diabetes
                treatment but may be prescribed off-label for weight loss at a
                healthcare provider's discretion. Wegovy® is FDA-approved for
                weight loss. Ozempic® and Wegovy® are the registered
                trademarks of Novo Nordisk A/S. Mounjaro® is a registered
                trademark of Eli Lilly and Company. 5MinuteMeds is not
                affiliated or endorsed by Novo Nordisk A/S or Eli Lilly and
                Company.
            </p>
            <p class="disclaimer">
                *The assessment on the 5MinuteMeds website does not create a doctor-patient relationship between you and 5MinuteMeds.
            </p>
            <p class="disclaimer">
                Beluga Health, a network of US-licensed physicians adhering to strict medical protocols for patient safety, has established criteria to determine GLP-1 treatment eligibility.
            </p>
            <p class="disclaimer">
                Your assessment responses determine initial eligibility for GLP-1 treatment, and a Beluga Health clinician will meet with you after checkout to confirm if a prescription is appropriate.
            </p>
            <p class="disclaimer">
                Beluga Health clinicians retain full prescribing authority for compounded GLP-1 medications.
            </p>
            <p class="disclaimer">
                All claims and results on this website reflect self-reported data from HeyFeels members following treatment plans that include compounded GLP-1 medications and medical consultations.
            </p>
            <p class="disclaimer">
                Members reported weight during initial medical intake and every 3-4 weeks during treatment. Individual results vary based on program adherence and following your clinician's recommendations.
