                Pharmacy Partners: We partner with multiple US-certified compounding pharmacies to ensure consistent quality and availability. Our team maintains regular communication with pharmacy partners regarding supply, shipping, and medication testing. *Individual results vary based on starting weight and program adherence. Measurements reflect changes in hips, waist, chest, thighs, and arms. Results shown represent members who combined treatment with healthy lifestyle changes. Your results may differ. Prescriptions are at your provider's medical discretion and may not be suitable for everyone. 5MinuteMeds members typically experience 1-2 lbs per week weight loss after 4 weeks when combining treatment with healthy habits. Always consult with a healthcare professional before starting any medication or weight loss program.
