                Medical treatment is provided by CareGLP Affiliated P.C.s and Beluga Health, affiliated networks of medical professional corporations.
            </p>
            <p class="disclaimer">
                All data, photos, and claims represent real 5MinuteMeds member experiences, not clinical trial results or public studies.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .footer {
        background-color: #1d1d1f;
        padding: 48px 80px 32px 80px;
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    }

    .footer-container {
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .footer-top {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 2fr;
        gap: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .footer-brand {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
    }

    .brand-name {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .brand-tagline {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #b3b3b3;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .social-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .social-link {
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: #b3b3b3;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .social-link:hover {
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .legitscript-badge {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .legitscript-badge img {
        width: 110px;
        height: auto;
    }

    .footer-nav {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 32px;
    }

    .nav-column h3 {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    }

    .nav-column ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
    }

    .nav-column a {
        color: #b3b3b3;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 14px;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .nav-column a:hover {
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .footer-divider {
        height: 1px;
        background-color: #333333;
        margin: 32px 0;
    }

    .footer-disclaimers {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
    }

    .disclaimer {
        font-size: 11px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #999999;
        margin: 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .footer-top {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .footer-nav {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        }

        .legitscript-badge {
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .footer {
            padding: 32px 20px 24px 20px;
        }

        .footer-top {
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .footer-nav {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .brand-name {
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .brand-tagline {
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .social-links {
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .social-link {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
        }

        .legitscript-badge img {
            width: 100px;
        }

        .nav-column h3 {
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .nav-column a {
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .footer-divider {
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .footer-disclaimers {
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .disclaimer {
            font-size: 10px;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .footer {
            padding: 24px 20px 20px 20px;
        }

        .nav-column h3 {
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .nav-column a {
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    }
</style>